NK016(ma)014:0: na rag dong sprugs phyag rgya gcig pa'i zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bzhugs so //
NK016(ma)014:1: na rag dong sprugs phyag rgya gcig pa la brten
NK016(ma)014:2: pa'i zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bklag chog nag 'gros su
NK016(ma)014:3: bkod par / bdag gi rnal 'byor phyag rgya gcig pa nyer bsdu'i bar song rjes /
NK016(ma)014:4: bdag gi thugs ka nas ram yam kham 'phros pas
NK016(ma)014:5: ma dag pa'i dngos 'dzin thams cad bsregs gtor sbyangs
NK016(ma)014:6: / stong pa'i ngang las bsang chu'i steng du /
NK016(ma)014:8: nyi ma la gnas pa'i h+au yig dmar po /
NK016(ma)014:12: badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h'u phata /
NK016(ma)014:13: khro mo dbang phyug ma dmar mo dril bu dang
NK016(ma)014:14: b+han dmar 'dzin pa'i skur gyur par bsam zhing rdo
NK016(ma)014:15: rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgyas reg la /
NK016(ma)014:16: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai sarba dra b+y+aam shwa d+ha ya +aahmh'u h+aihth+aa /
NK016(ma)014:17: brgya rtsa brgyad kyis byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK016(ma)014:18: khro mo dbang phyug ma'i rang bzhin gyi chu'i rdul phra rab tu gyur par bsam /
NK016(ma)014:19: ma h+aa kro d+hi sha r+ai sarba dra b+y+aam shwa d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK016(ma)014:20: ces bdag gnas yo byad thams cad la bsang gtor bya zhing /
NK016(ma)014:21: thog mtha' kun tu bsang gtor gyi bya ba thams cad 'dis bya'o //
NK016(ma)014:22: gang du bya ba'i sa chog dang zhi ba'i thab dkyil spyi ltar la /
NK016(ma)014:24: g.yas phyogs rdzas stegs pad dkar 'dab brgyad kyi lte
NK016(ma)014:25: bar ba las byung ba'i mar khu dgang blugs kyi
NK016(ma)014:26: gzar bu kha sbyar dang bcas pa /
NK016(ma)014:27: mdun gyi 'dab mar 'o ma can gyi rtse mo'i
NK016(ma)014:28: cha las byung ba'i yam shing mtho gang ba rtse
NK016(ma)014:30: pad 'dab lhag ma bdun la til dkar /
NK016(ma)014:33: nas dkar dang 'bras dkar gyi chan sogs kha zas dkar po dang /
NK016(ma)014:34: tsan+dana dkar po sogs dri dkar po'i rigs dang /
NK016(ma)014:35: tsam pa ka sogs me tog dkar po'i rigs te thams cad rang bzhin nam bcos pas dkar pa /
NK016(ma)014:36: thugs dam bskur ba'i rdzas yungs kar rnams rin po che dkar po'i snod du bsham /
NK016(ma)014:37: g.yon phyogs mchod stegs pad dkar 'dab brgyad lte bar /
NK016(ma)014:38: 'o ma 'bras chan dngul phye me tog dkar po
NK016(ma)014:39: rnams dang bsres pa'i mar dkar kyi 'das gtor zlum
NK016(ma)014:40: po ril bu drug gis bskor ba many+dzi'i steng bkod
NK016(ma)014:41: pa'i mdun du rgyu de las 'jig rten pa'i gtor
NK016(ma)014:42: ma dkar zlum / mdun gyi pad 'dab la rdor dril /
NK016(ma)014:43: de'i g.yas g.yon gyi 'dab mar sman raka /
NK016(ma)014:44: pad 'dab lhag ma lnga la zhabs bsil dang bzhi
NK016(ma)014:45: bsnol kyi mchod rdzas rang bzhin nam bcos pas dkar
NK016(ma)014:48: thab kyi mdun du stan dkar zhing 'jam pa la
NK016(ma)014:49: slob dpon chas gos dang rin po che'i rgyan dkar
NK016(ma)014:50: pos brgyan pa rdo rje skyil krung gis shing pa'i
NK016(ma)014:51: phyogs su kha bltas pas 'dug nas /
NK016(ma)014:52: don gyi sems chos thams cad kyi gshis lugs lhag
NK016(ma)014:53: pa bden pa dbyer med kyi lta ba rtogs shing
NK016(ma)014:54: byang chub kyi sems dang ldan pas kun slong stangs
NK016(ma)014:55: kyi sems bcas dang rang bzhin gyi sdig ltung dam
NK016(ma)014:56: tshig nyams chag rnams sbyong bar 'dod pa'i sems zhi
NK016(ma)014:58: ngag sngags rnams phra zhing zhib la rgyun mi 'chad
NK016(ma)014:59: par bzla ba'i tshul gyi cho ga'i las la 'jug
NK016(ma)014:60: ste / rdo rje thabs kyi rang bzhin ye shes lnga'i ngo bo /
NK016(ma)014:61: dril bu shes rab kyi rang bzhin stong nyid chos kyi sgra dbyangs sgrogs pa /
NK016(ma)014:62: gnyis ka'ang don dam pa byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin no //
NK016(ma)014:64: badz+ra gan+de +aah sarba ta th+aa sogs kyis sngags rgyas dam tshig gsum dran par bya'o //
NK016(ma)014:65: de nas phyi mchod rnams bsang sbyang /
NK016(ma)014:66: stong pa'i ngang las mchod snod dbyings kyi zhing khams
NK016(ma)014:67: bsam gyis mi khyab par 'khor 'das kyi rtsi bcud
NK016(ma)014:68: thams cad bsdus nas mchod rdzas rnams la thim par
NK016(ma)014:69: gyur / na mahsaman+ta sogs bzhi bsnol sngags bcas dang /
NK016(ma)014:70: sman raka gnyis sngags tsam gyis byin gyis brlab bo //
NK016(ma)014:71: las gtor sreg rdzas rnams la bsang chu 'thor zhing /
NK016(ma)014:72: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai sogs dang /
NK016(ma)014:74: stong pa'i ngang las ma dang a las nyi zla'i
NK016(ma)014:75: ga'u'i snod du rang gi thugs ka nas gtor ma'i
NK016(ma)014:76: gnas su 'bru gsum dang sreg rdzas kyi gnas su
NK016(ma)014:77: 'bru lnga spros te 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa
NK016(ma)014:78: las zhi ba'i las gtor rin po che'i mchod sdong
NK016(ma)014:80: sreg rdzas rnams ro brgya ldan pa'i zag med ye
NK016(ma)014:81: shes kyi bdud rtsi nam mkha' gang bas zhi ba'i
NK016(ma)014:82: las sgrub pa la thogs pa med pa'i nus pa
NK016(ma)014:83: dang ldan par gyur bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)014:86: zhes bzlas pas byin gyis brlab /
NK016(ma)014:88: stong pa'i ngang las mdun na h'u las zhi ba'i
NK016(ma)014:89: thab khung dkar zhing zlum pa kha khyer bang rim
NK016(ma)014:90: gsum dang ldan pa 'od zer dkar po 'phro bar
NK016(ma)014:91: gyur / rang gi thugs ka nas ram yig thab
NK016(ma)014:92: nang du spros ye shes kyi me 'od dkar po
NK016(ma)014:94: ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)014:95: ces rgyun bzhag gam gtsub shing las byung ba'i me du ba med pa sbar la /
NK016(ma)014:96: thab gyi me'i dbus su ma dang dihls byung ba'i
NK016(ma)014:97: nyi ma dang ra skyes kyi gdan la yig dkar
NK016(ma)014:98: po 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las ag+ni de
NK016(ma)014:100: zhi ba'i me lha dkar po zhi zhing 'dzum pa
NK016(ma)014:101: drang srong gi cha byad can gun+d+he dang bgrang 'phreng
NK016(ma)014:105: thugs ka'i h+au las 'od zer 'phros pas shar lho nas me lha 'khor bcas bzhengs par bsam la /
NK016(ma)014:106: ag+ne de wa sa ma ya h'u dzah zhes se gol bsnol mar gdab /
NK016(ma)014:108: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK016(ma)014:109: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs 'byung po che //
NK016(ma)014:110: me lha drang srong bram ze mchog /
NK016(ma)014:111: 'di nyid du ni gshegs su gsol //
NK016(ma)014:113: ag+ne de wa ri shi dzahdzahsa spyan drang /
NK016(ma)014:118: me lha zhal cung zad gdangs pas sreg blugs kyi
NK016(ma)014:119: bdud rtsi'i rgyun drangs nas gsol bar bsam la lag
NK016(ma)014:120: gnyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i khu tshur du byas pas
NK016(ma)014:123: zhes g.yas pa'i blugs gzar bdun gyis g.yon pa'i dgang
NK016(ma)014:124: gzar bkang rjes gzar bu kha sbyar te pus mo'i
NK016(ma)014:125: nang las mi 'da' bar g.yas bskor gyis /
NK016(ma)014:126: ag+ni de wa ri shi ha bya ka bya di
NK016(ma)014:127: bya bdag cag dpon slob 'khor dang bcas pa'i dam
NK016(ma)014:128: tshig nyams chag rtog sgrib thams cad sh+ain+tam ku ru
NK016(ma)014:129: s+w+aa h+aa / zhes lan gsum gyis dgang blugs phul /
NK016(ma)014:130: de rjes sngags de kho nas yam shing /
NK016(ma)014:132: sregs rdzas rnams re re nas sngags 'dod gsol bcas lnga'am bdun sogs ji ltar rigs pa phul la /
NK016(ma)014:134: de bzhin rigs las grub pa yi //
NK016(ma)014:135: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK016(ma)014:136: phrin las kun gyi dpang po 'dzad //
NK016(ma)014:140: ma mo rig pa'i rgyal po khyod kyis las thams
NK016(ma)014:141: cad byed pas sreg rdzas lha'i zhal du 'bul ba
NK016(ma)014:142: dang / me nyid ye shes kyi mer byin gyis
NK016(ma)014:143: brlabs nas bdag sogs sems can thams cad kyi rtog
NK016(ma)014:144: sgrib dam tshig nyams chag thams cad zhi ba'i phrin
NK016(ma)014:148: me lha 'bar ba'i rnam par bsam /
NK016(ma)014:149: de dag sbyin lha ste 'jig rten pa'i me lha mchod pa'i cho ga'o //
NK016(ma)014:150: de nas sreg lha zhes 'das pa'i me lha mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)014:151: phyag rgya gcig pa'i gzhung ltar /
NK016(ma)014:152: thab kyi me'i dbus su e las nam mkha' sogs nas /
NK016(ma)014:153: cha shas yongs su rdzogs par gyur /
NK016(ma)014:155: bdag gi thugs ka nas a dkar po dri ma
NK016(ma)014:156: med pa dwangs shing gsal ba spros zla ba'i gdan
NK016(ma)014:158: me lha bcom ldan 'das sogs nas /
NK016(ma)014:159: byin gyis brlab pa'i bar bya /
NK016(ma)014:160: bdag mdun gyi thugs kar dwangs ma'i srog sogs /
NK016(ma)014:163: ye shes kyi 'khor lo dam tshig pa dang dbyer med gyur //
NK016(ma)014:164: dngos su 'byor dang kun tu bzang po mkha' dbyings
NK016(ma)014:165: rnam dag phyi nang gsang ba'i sogs kyis spyir mchod
NK016(ma)014:166: nas / bye brag tu kun bzang /
NK016(ma)014:169: sman raka gtor ma sngags tsam gyis 'bul /
NK016(ma)014:171: dkyil 'khor gyi lha cung zad 'dzum pa'i ljags rdo
NK016(ma)014:172: rje 'od kyi sbu gu can gyis sreg blugs kyi
NK016(ma)014:173: bdud rtsi'i rgyun drangs nas gsol bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)014:174: badz+ra sa t+wa +aah zhes pa bdun gyi bkang nas yig brgya la /
NK016(ma)014:176: bdag dang sem can thams cad dang khyad par sbyin
NK016(ma)014:177: pa'i bdag po'i nad gdon sdig sgrib dam tshig nyams
NK016(ma)014:178: chag nyes ltung thams cad sh+ain+tam ku ru s+w+aa h+aa
NK016(ma)014:180: da ha da ha sogs ngan song gnas 'dren sngags dang /
NK016(ma)014:181: dmigs yul tshe las 'das pa'i nyams chag sdig ltung
NK016(ma)014:182: sbyang zhing 'khor ba dang ngan 'gro'i 'jigs pa las
NK016(ma)014:184: zhes spel tshig dang bcas pas lan gsum 'bul /
NK016(ma)014:185: de nas yam shing mar khu sogs bsreg rdzas gzhan rnams yig brgya la sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)014:186: btags pas grangs bsags mthar spel tshig sngar ltar sbyar nas 'bul te /
NK016(ma)014:187: dbang mchog rgyal po'i rgyud gyi sbyin sreg skabs /
NK016(ma)014:188: thugs sgrub phrin las rnam bzhi la //
NK016(ma)014:189: na rag dong sprugs gdon par bya //
NK016(ma)014:190: kun kyang de ru 'dus pa yin //
NK016(ma)014:191: lha brgya sngags brgya bshags pa tshang //
NK016(ma)014:192: rgya bar sh+aan+tim ku ru gdags //
NK016(ma)014:194: ro sreg lta bu'i tshe zhun mar gyi skong mdzad cing /
NK016(ma)014:196: ma 'grub na'ang chad pa'i skyon med do //
NK016(ma)014:198: badz+ra sat+wa +aahl gtor sngags btags pas las gtor dang /
NK016(ma)014:200: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa his sman raka phul nas sngar bzhin bstod la /
NK016(ma)014:202: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK016(ma)014:203: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i sbyin sreg 'bul //
NK016(ma)014:204: bdag gi zhi ba'i phrin las mthar phyin nas //
NK016(ma)014:205: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par mdzod //
NK016(ma)014:207: lha tshogs rnams kyi sku las 'od zer dkar po
NK016(ma)014:208: 'phros bsgrub bya la reg pas dam tshig nyams chag
NK016(ma)014:209: rtog sgrib thams cad zhi bar bsam mo //
NK016(ma)014:210: de nas gtang rag gi mchod bstod dang bzod gsol byas la ye shes pa //
NK016(ma)014:211: khyed kyis sems can sogs kyis gshegs /
NK016(ma)014:212: dam tshig pa bdag nyid la thim par bsam /
NK016(ma)014:214: ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h'u phata /
NK016(ma)014:215: ces blugs gzar gyi mar khus me gsos te 'jig
NK016(ma)014:216: rten pa'i me lha sngar bzhin gsal bar bsam la
NK016(ma)014:217: / ag+ne de wa ri shi ha bya sogs kyis bsreg rdzas lhag rnams 'bul /
NK016(ma)014:219: sngags mthar las gtor dang sman raka 'bul /
NK016(ma)014:222: badz+ra muhs ye shes pa rang gnas su gshegs /
NK016(ma)014:223: dam tshig pa 'bar ba'i rnam par gyur par bsam
NK016(ma)014:224: las kyi rjes bsdu zhing bsngo shis kyis mtha' brgyan
NK016(ma)014:225: par bya'o // zhes nyer 'kho'i bklag chog tu blo gros nas bskul bzhin /
NK016(ma)014:226: pra dz+ny+aas gzhung zin ltar bsgrigs pa dge legs 'phel //
